data.description: This downtown Puyallup home just hit the market! This historical home is move-in ready with modern amenities like forced air. Your front door opens into a large living room with refinished hardwood floors and wood burning fireplace. Living room flows into kitchen with dishwasher, oven and refrigerator included! Two bedrooms and full bathroom are downstairs with double closets in your primary room. Head upstairs and you'll find two more large bedrooms with a half bathroom. Exterior has been freshly painted with new windows! Oversized detached garage and ample parking behind home. Fully fenced & large lot! Location, location, location! Check out the virtual tour!
